{"tid":1884486,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【武漢肺炎】王家衛新作《繁花》延期開拍","createTime":"2020-02-17T15:24:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-19T04:22:40.000Z","uid":134071,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4a19b01294f4c391e1c0881fe22c3c6d9e24e694","tid":1884486,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T15:24:27.000Z","msg":"睇套《擺渡人》都知王家衛回哂塘 &nbsp;<br />\n(王家衛唔係掛名導演, 但王家衛親自執導《擺渡人》大部分場面, 已經係公開秘密)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200217/54RMLPPTPS2CGEWMH4ATE2UO6Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200217%2F54RMLPPTPS2CGEWMH4ATE2UO6Q%2F&d=rocWq0H159RMtn9QCTPVbHG9l5Y5fMjkJfB04Oq%2Bkmk%3D&h=77ff378d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200217%2F54RMLPPTPS2CGEWMH4ATE2UO6Q%2F&h=f31a2a79\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200217/54RMLPPTPS2CGEWMH4ATE2UO6Q/</a><br />\n<br />\n【武漢肺炎】王家衛新作《繁花》受疫情影響 延期至暑假後開拍<br />\n1小時前<br />\n<br />\n澤東公司之前宣佈王家衛今年會監製金宇澄創作的長篇小說《繁花》的網劇和親自執導電影版，日前廣電總局備案公示中劇集版已取得開拍批文，原本預計下個月中上海開機，全劇共30集，男主角是胡歌，女主角是曾參演《慶餘年》的辛芷蕾，據知電影版和劇集版開拍時間僅差幾個月，影視兩版男主角都是胡歌，至於電影版女主角有傳是章子怡。不過現因武漢肺炎熱肆虐，上海疫情也是相當嚴重關係，影視版都叫停了，最快要等暑假後才開拍。<br />\n<br />\n《繁》的劇集版將由《天盛長歌》導演沈嚴執導，故事以10歲的阿寶開始，以中年的小毛去世結束，描寫了兩個時間段的上海，一是20世紀六、七十年代，一是八、九十年代，尤其是這兩個特殊歷史時期上海人的生存狀況。"},{"pid":"703489cbde11c965ae43d5693ad2a2d179e4fb80","tid":1884486,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T15:24:42.000Z","msg":"壹週刊 - 1350期<br />\n<br />\n探熱針<br />\n王家衞落場執手尾  Angelababy等運到<br />\n.....<br />\n內地很多作家做埋導演，由暢銷小說《從你的全世界路過》其中一章《擺渡人》改編的，亦由原著作者張嘉佳親自執導，王家衞負責監製。導演新手，<strong>開工不夠兩星期，王大導便親自落場，收拾殘局。</strong><br />\n<br />\n「導演冇經驗，鏡頭、燈光點擺都唔清唔楚，就算高佬（王家衞）經常落場教路，但始終拍唔到佢嘅心水，與其拖落去，高佬決定自己拍番。」一名劇組工作人員透露。"},{"pid":"dbe3f26b131da8ecda71e88fac2fbcabe1a3b264","tid":1884486,"uid":63311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T15:25:26.000Z","msg":"有冇馬沙？"},{"pid":"b49ffebbb3d13431b905644e13429ad693567342","tid":1884486,"uid":61284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T15:27:26.000Z","msg":"同一部同一個導演又拍劇又拍電影？"},{"pid":"d08103b1488b700e779a6a98b956bf9384ae9b29","tid":1884486,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b49ffebbb3d13431b905644e13429ad693567342","tid":1884486,"uid":61284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T15:27:26.000Z","msg":"同一部同一個導演又拍劇又拍電影？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T15:30:19.000Z","msg":"劇集版由王家衛監製, 沈嚴導演"},{"pid":"cad7168524977bd7ffd2c968b1e0979b975c20df","tid":1884486,"uid":313584,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T15:31:10.000Z","msg":"今次要拍幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca82a3cc7f53b3e9e7b4df473991e252a183d34b","tid":1884486,"uid":134071,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"cad7168524977bd7ffd2c968b1e0979b975c20df","tid":1884486,"uid":313584,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T15:31:10.000Z","msg":"今次要拍幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T15:35:57.000Z","msg":"如果係搵錢戲, 好快拍哂<br />\n《擺渡人》一年內拍完兼上映"},{"pid":"7df04aa47de658fa9104167617d7b7cb27453720","tid":1884486,"uid":313584,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ca82a3cc7f53b3e9e7b4df473991e252a183d34b","tid":1884486,"uid":134071,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"cad7168524977bd7ffd2c968b1e0979b975c20df","tid":1884486,"uid":313584,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T15:31:10.000Z","msg":"今次要拍幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T15:35:57.000Z","msg":"如果係搵錢戲, 好快拍哂<br />\n《擺渡人》一年內拍完兼上映"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T15:38:48.000Z","msg":"擺渡人唔係張嘉佳導演咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"